  "200 N/m": "200海里/米",
  "The stretch is 0.06 m. Work = (1/2)k*x^2, so 12 = (1/2)k(0.06)^2 = (1/2)k(0.0036). Therefore k = 24/0.0036 = 6667 N/m (approximately).": "伸展面积为0.06米。工作=(1/2)k*x__2,所以12=(1/2)k(0.06)__2 =(1/2)k(0.0036),因此k = 24/0.0036 = 6667 N/m(约合)。",
