  "Work done by gravity = mgh = 2(9.8)(10) = 196 J. Gravity does positive work when an object falls because the force and displacement are in the same direction.": "重力 = mgh = 2(9.8)(10) = 196 J. 当物体坠落时,由于力和位移方向相同,重力确实起到积极作用。",
  "What is the elastic potential energy stored in a spring compressed 0.3 m with spring constant k = 500 N/m?": "以弹簧常数K=500牛顿/米储存在弹簧压缩0.3米、弹簧常数K=500牛顿时的弹性潜在能量是多少?",
